QuestData.Title: Close Enough
QuestData.Description:
<Oculeth's eyes have dulled. His voice trembles.>
Are we... are we close?
So hungry...
QuestData.LogDescription: Carry Chief Telemancer Oculeth to Thalyssra in Shal'Aran.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for recovering Oculeth. He will be an invaluable asset to our cause.
